Dandelion,Text,Similarity,API,is,a,semantic,sentence,similarity,API,optimized,on,short,sentences,written,in,several,languages,Italian,English,German,Portuguese,and,French,at,the,moment,With,this,API,users,are,able,to,compare,two,sentences,and,get,a,score,of,a,semantic,similarity,It,works,even,if,the,two,sentences,don,t,have,any,word,in,common,and,it,accepts,also,URLs,as,input,values